{"article_id":"9T9tXRcVaUik4iFy","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The painful public collapse Friday of Paul Ryan 's biggest endeavor as House speaker","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"- legislation","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"to unwind the Democratic health care law","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"he and his party spent years castigating as a disaster -","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"dealt a serious blow to the Wisconsin Republican .","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"But","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"as embarrassing a setback as this was","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"- Obamacare is here to stay `` for the foreseeable future , ''","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"Ryan conceded -","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"he is n't going anywhere .","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"No one is prepared to challenge Ryan for his job ,","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"said GOP lawmakers from across the Republican Conference .","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"While some right-wing media and outside groups are agitating to replace the speaker ,","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"and his antagonists on the White House staff needle him anonymously in the press ,","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"there is no way","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"he will be ousted .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"President Donald Trump has n't turned on him , either -","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"at least not yet .","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"And Ryan remains popular with his rank-and-file members ,","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"who genuinely like him .","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"Critically , Ryan is not a liability for them back home , the ultimate litmus test for any congressional leader .","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"Yet the debacle over the American Health Care Act showed how the promise of Ryan as speaker has failed to live up to the reality .","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"When he took over for former Speaker John Boehner in November 2015","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"following an uprising by conservatives ,","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"Ryan was seen as the one figure","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"who could heal the divisions within the GOP Conference , especially with the hard-line Freedom Caucus .","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"That has n't happened ,","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"to put it mildly .","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"Ryan is still struggling with the same stubborn political dynamic","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"that torpedoed Boehner 's career .","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"On big issues ,","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"if Ryan gives into the Freedom Caucus ,","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"he alienates more moderate members of his party","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"and loses any ability","depth":13},{"id":34,"text":"to work with Democrats .","depth":13},{"id":35,"text":"If he tries to cut a deal with Democrats and his own moderates ,","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"the Freedom Caucus goes ballistic ,","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"attacking him in tandem with its allies in right-wing media and conservative outside groups .","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"Having a Republican in the White House was supposed to finally tame the group .","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"It was easy to blow up deals","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"Republicans were attempting to cut with Barack Obama ;","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"Donald Trump ,","depth":13},{"id":42,"text":"the thinking went ,","depth":13},{"id":43,"text":"would never tolerate it .","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"The health-care debate showed","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"how wrong that was .","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"`` He 's a really nice guy , a really smart guy , ''","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"said a veteran GOP lawmaker","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"who asked not to be named .","depth":13},{"id":49,"text":"But `` he ca n't seal the deal ,","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"which is a real problem . ''","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"Even with Trump , the `` ultimate closer , '' in the White House .","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"Things wo n't get any easier for Ryan .","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"He will now have to find a way","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"to deliver on Trump 's border wall ,","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"which Democrats have vowed to block .","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"The possibility of a government shutdown looms in late April and again in October","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"unless Republicans can figure out how to keep funding going .","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"The debt ceiling has to be increased this summer , always a tough vote for GOP lawmakers .","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"An expensive infrastructure package","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"that conservatives hate","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"will require Democratic buy-in .","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"That 's to say nothing of the next daunting item on the GOP to-do list , tax reform","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"- arguably tougher to pull off than health-care legislation .","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"Ryan put his personal prestige on the line","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"to pass his health care legislation ,","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"publicly and privately exhorting his colleagues to support it .","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"Ryan became the face of the legislation ,","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"figuring","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"he could sell it better than anyone else .","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"In the end , enough of his own members rejected the proposal","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"to bring it down .","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"After being forced to pull the bill ,","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"Ryan deployed many of the same lines","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"he 's been using for months","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"to explain away failures or setbacks .","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"Republicans are suffering the `` growing pains ''","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"of going from being the opposition party to the majority ,","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"`` Doing big things is hard , ''","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"the speaker said ,","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"adding","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"that Republicans want `` to improve people 's lives ,","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"and we will . ''","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"Yet there was also a somber tone .","depth":6},{"id":85,"text":"Ryan did n't try to hide from blame ,","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"and he warned his own GOP colleagues","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"that they better find a way","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"to compromise .","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"`` I will not sugarcoat it ,","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"this was a disappointing day for us ...","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"This is a setback ,","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"no two ways about it , ''","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"Ryan told reporters","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"after pulling the bill from the floor in the face of certain defeat .","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"`` All of us ,","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"myself included ,","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"will need time","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"to reflect on how we got to this moment ,","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"what we could have done","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"to do better . ''","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"Ryan added :","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"`` But ultimately , this all kind of comes down to a choice .","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"Are all of us willing to give a little","depth":14},{"id":104,"text":"to get something done ?","depth":14},{"id":105,"text":"Are we willing to say yes to the good , to the very good ,","depth":14},{"id":106,"text":"even if it 's not the perfect ?","depth":14},{"id":107,"text":"Because","depth":13},{"id":108,"text":"if we 're willing to do that ,","depth":14},{"id":109,"text":"there remains an incredible opportunity in front of us . ''","depth":14},{"id":110,"text":"Ryan said","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"he did n't `` want to cast blame '' for who lost health care ,","depth":7},{"id":112,"text":"but he then went on to blame the Freedom Caucus","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"- which he called `` their team '' -","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"for bringing down his bill .","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"`` There is a block of 'no ' votes","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"that we had ,","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"that is why this did n't pass , ''","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"Ryan said .","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"`` Some of the members of that caucus were voting with us","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"but not enough were .","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"I met with their chairman earlier today ,","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"and he made it clear to me","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"that the votes were n't going to be there from their team .","depth":12},{"id":124,"text":"That was sufficient","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"to have this bill not pass . ''","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"Trump , for his part , praised Ryan","depth":7},{"id":127,"text":"despite the failure","depth":8},{"id":128,"text":"to pass the health care bill ,","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"which leaves Obamacare in place as the law of the land .","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"`` I like Speaker Ryan .","depth":9},{"id":131,"text":"He worked very hard , ''","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"Trump told reporters in the White House","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"after the bill was pulled .","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"`` I 'm not going to speak badly about anybody within the Republican Party .","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"Certainly there 's a history ,","depth":9},{"id":136,"text":"but I really think","depth":9},{"id":137,"text":"Paul worked hard . ''","depth":9},{"id":138,"text":"Freedom Caucus members said","depth":7},{"id":139,"text":"they do n't blame Ryan for the failure ,","depth":8},{"id":140,"text":"at least not publicly .","depth":8},{"id":141,"text":"\" Paul Ryan , he ' a very good man .","depth":9},{"id":142,"text":"He ' s an eloquent speaker .","depth":10},{"id":143,"text":"He is an excellent representative of the GOP Conference as a whole , ''","depth":10},{"id":144,"text":"said Rep. Mo Brooks","depth":9},{"id":145,"text":"( R-Ala. ) .","depth":9},{"id":146,"text":"`` I like the job","depth":9},{"id":147,"text":"he ' s doing","depth":9},{"id":148,"text":"and I want him to stay as speaker of the House .","depth":9},{"id":149,"text":"And I ' ve heard nothing to the contrary . ''","depth":9},{"id":150,"text":"Other rank-and-file members were equally supportive","depth":5},{"id":151,"text":"as they left town","depth":6},{"id":152,"text":"to lick their wounds .","depth":6},{"id":153,"text":"Sign up here for Huddle","depth":5},{"id":154,"text":"A daily play-by-play of congressional news in your inbox .","depth":5},{"id":155,"text":"Email Sign Up","depth":5},{"id":156,"text":"By signing up","depth":7},{"id":157,"text":"you agree to receive email newsletters or alerts from .","depth":7},{"id":158,"text":"You can unsubscribe at any time .","depth":6},{"id":159,"text":"`` If you know of someone","depth":7},{"id":160,"text":"who cares more ,","depth":8},{"id":161,"text":"works harder ,","depth":9},{"id":162,"text":"who ' s brighter ,","depth":10},{"id":163,"text":"who ' s more committed to lead this institution ,","depth":10},{"id":164,"text":"give me their name , ''","depth":6},{"id":165,"text":"said Rep . Rob Woodall","depth":7},{"id":166,"text":"( R-Ala. ) ,","depth":7},{"id":167,"text":"a Ryan loyalist .","depth":6},{"id":168,"text":"`` We go through leaders","depth":6},{"id":169,"text":"like we ' re changing shirts .","depth":6},{"id":170,"text":"I don ' t think","depth":7},{"id":171,"text":"it reflects on the leadership ,","depth":7},{"id":172,"text":"I think","depth":7},{"id":173,"text":"it reflects on us . \"","depth":7},{"id":174,"text":"Yet Ryan faces the prospect for the rest of this Congress","depth":6},{"id":175,"text":"- unless he moves decisively to the middle -","depth":6},{"id":176,"text":"that members may need to get signoff from the Freedom Caucus and its chairman , Rep. Mark Meadows","depth":8},{"id":177,"text":"( R-N.C. ) ,","depth":8},{"id":178,"text":"before they move major legislation .","depth":7},{"id":179,"text":"Or at least to know","depth":7},{"id":180,"text":"that the Freedom Caucus wo n't try to kill their bill .","depth":7},{"id":181,"text":"It 's a dynamic","depth":5},{"id":182,"text":"that will be a huge challenge for Ryan","depth":6},{"id":183,"text":"as he tries to get past the Obamacare reversal .","depth":6},{"id":184,"text":"Both Ryan and Trump emphasized","depth":5},{"id":185,"text":"they want to move quickly on to tax reform ,","depth":6},{"id":186,"text":"although the failure","depth":9},{"id":187,"text":"to replace Obamacare","depth":9},{"id":188,"text":"leaves them with $ 1 trillion less","depth":9},{"id":189,"text":"to use for that fight ,","depth":9},{"id":190,"text":"as there will be less room","depth":8},{"id":191,"text":"to cut taxes","depth":9},{"id":192,"text":"without ballooning the deficit .","depth":9},{"id":193,"text":"`` Yes , this does make tax reform more difficult ,","depth":7},{"id":194,"text":"but it does not in any way make it impossible , ''","depth":7},{"id":195,"text":"Ryan acknowledged .","depth":6},{"id":196,"text":"But Ryan , a former chairman of the Ways and Means Committe , said","depth":7},{"id":197,"text":"it will be easier to get Republicans to agree on taxes than on health care .","depth":7},{"id":198,"text":"`` I do n't think","depth":8},{"id":199,"text":"this is prologue for other future things","depth":8},{"id":200,"text":"because there are other parts of our agenda","depth":8},{"id":201,"text":"that people have even more agreement on what to achieve . ''","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":403,"left":354,"right":402,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":354,"left":222,"right":353,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":222,"left":206,"right":221,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":206,"left":205,"right":4,"relation":"same-unit","nuc